{"tid":1594952,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"因應聯合國的會見, 有 7 項新的-美國白宮聯署-產生, 希望大家用力推.!!!!","createTime":"2019-09-25T22:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T14:40:24.000Z","uid":324576,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4b4c6e3fc92a560e914e175b6784d743e074a3a7","tid":1594952,"uid":324576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T22:42:37.000Z","msg":"(20190926)<br />\n致各位 深愛香港的香港人.<br />\n美國總統特朗普 已在聯合國中, 特別開名出聲, 敦促中國信守中英聯合聲明保障香港自由, 大家經過3個多月的&quot;反送中運動&quot;, 亦明白-10月1日國慶的前後, 表態運動的階段亦已進入白熱化!!<br />\n<br />\n在此, 希望大家再多出一分力, 把握機會, 把下列<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">《美國白宮聯署》</span></strong>簽署作實. 好讓美國在聯合國會議中, 與各國見面時, 可進行商討, 使香港聲音可以籍美國在聯合國會中發揮. <br />\n<br />\n請幫忙分享及廣傳~<br />\n新一輪議案(<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">有 6 項</span></strong>), 加以停止 中共政府, 港共政府, 香港警察, 對香港及香港市民一連串的迫害行為. 並把意圖離開香港政府及港共警察的人士, 加以限制. <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">簽署後, 大家會收到回覆 Email 作實.</span></strong><br />\n~每一議案, 都會產生單一專屬的 Email/電郵 以作回覆, 所以若答應了以上<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 6 項的議案</span>, 便會產生<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"> 6 </span></strong>個不同名目的相對電郵回覆, 以作核實. 因應部份電郵系統名單的設定, 可能只會顯示 <strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後或最近</span></strong> 的電郵名稱, 因而錯過了較早時間, 其他電郵回覆. 故請小心核對.<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">*記得檢查email , 並請按 confirm your signature by clicking here 確認*</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 請美國行使《全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法》，制裁侵犯人權的香港官員或知名人士。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2mIGUn2&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=682210c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2mIGUn2</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 請求美國派美軍前往香港，拯救正被香港警察濫捕、禁錮、虐打、性侵的香港市民。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kk2ZHW&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=bdf69eed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kk2ZHW</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 請求美國通過《香港保護法案》，暫停向香港警察出售催淚彈、胡椒噴霧、橡膠子彈和其他防暴物品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2m39jUJ&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=a33758fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2m39jUJ</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 請將香港警察加入《香港人權及民主法案》的制裁名單。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kyBsT1&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=c87da018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kyBsT1</a><br />\n<br />\n5. 請求美國禁止香港警察移民或入境美國。(針對黑警聯署第3彈!)<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kNkwbN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kNkwbN&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7163c0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kNkwbN</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 請求美國承認香港為美國保護區。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kK8y2q&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=7f99071b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kK8y2q</a><br />\n<br />\n較早時間合大家之力, 聯署的多份議案, 已在美國國會商討中, 加上黃之鋒, 何韻詩, 張崑陽等已在美國國會發言, 成效大家有目共睹, 所以大家不要放棄, 很多議案已經因為大家的發聲, 產生了影響力. <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山, 齊上齊落<br />\n香港人, 加油."},{"pid":"48cb9ba187e90dddd87039cec9be6262597d5c36","tid":1594952,"uid":243011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:18:30.000Z","msg":"目標 光復連登<br />\n係連登進行洗地 將行動Post推返上水面<br />\n<br />\n行動須知：<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1477804389/4094\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1477804389%2F4094&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=43c5a4af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1477804389/4094</a><br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFiup86nz72lh1uH4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFiup86nz72lh1uH4w&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=ac43bc98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFiup86nz72lh1uH4w</a><br />\n合作夥伴 HKREV：<a href=\"https://t.me/c/1477804389/4104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fc%2F1477804389%2F4104&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=f76494c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/c/1477804389/4104</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkrev.info/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkrev.info%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=61d462b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkrev.info/</a>"},{"pid":"4d709076f5e1056612a2513869a9862cde23102c","tid":1594952,"uid":243011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:21:12.000Z","msg":"第二點，我有保留，但其他，十分認同"},{"pid":"b26253985d89cbe509cd571e693d2bd58b69d9cb","tid":1594952,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T23:29:29.000Z","msg":"第二點有保留<br />\n美軍冇可能做到咁出面"},{"pid":"569213626ce41932543874b39c6867db7777a86d","tid":1594952,"uid":205687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:02:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d272fff6db64b2f7b9325b5a8ac79f4b13855c8d","tid":1594952,"uid":199502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:13:50.000Z","msg":"推推推推推簽曬佢喇！"},{"pid":"3359843436f7eeae8e81bc65ac707949b3281361","tid":1594952,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:17:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65d7975bfc2de4114ba218ecd74e042461a2544b","tid":1594952,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"2同6<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b0d86981ff9438b28c84877231902150e05260","tid":1594952,"uid":105353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3985848fef1519e8449835e0a3035